     1→/**
     2→ * Integration Routes
     3→ *
     4→ * REST endpoints for Maximo integration, including:
     5→ * - Webhook receiver for CM status updates from Maximo
     6→ * - Sync operations (push, pull, full)
     7→ * - Conflict management
     8→ * - Sync statistics
     9→ *
    10→ * Integration flow:
    11→ * 1. Maximo sends webhook on WO status change → POST /integration/webhooks/maximo
